      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STILTON SHINE (8) missed the frame latest when fifth at this track (29.88) but was a winner three back in the second best time of the program. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Can make amends. RIPPER JOE (3) three runs back produced a speedy 29.87 win over 520m at this track then has found the minor money in two runs since. Expected to feature on best figures. ZIPPING BUFFALO (6) has a strong record here including two wins from three starts. Recorded a nose win (29.71) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Can hit the frame with the right run. GYPSY GRACE (7) did a good job to finish second last time out over 520m at Nowra (29.65) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide.",
